parameters:
\SE\SE[50]Hmm, I apologize for summoning you here! It seems you
were in the middle of enjoying yourself, so I feel quite guilty
about it...

\SE[46]As for me, I want the activities of the citizens to
continue more and more! \SE[17]When you return, I hope you will
continue to strive!

\SE\SE[3]Hmm! Well then, let's get to the main topic! \SE[3]Have
you already heard about the Four Trials?

\SE[2]No... It's the first time I've heard of it. \SE[3]What kind
of trials are they?

\SE\SE[52]As I thought! The ritual passed down through
generations to bestow power upon those who overcome the trials,
huh!

\SE[9]I want all of you to overcome them and obtain power!
\SE[52]It's the special secret of Ulysseene. I'm sure you'll
experience a tremendous power-up...!

\SE\SE[100]Power-up...!? \!\SE[100]I wonder if even I can become
stronger...?

\SE\SE[52]Well, that's a special secret after all...! \SE[52]It
would be best to check the details at the Guild!!

\SE[14]The Four Trials... huh. \SE[15]It's a common theme, but...
it's nice, isn't it...!

The Four Trials have been unlocked. You can obtain enhancements
specific to each location. Let's try going around in any order
you like!

The 'Fourth Trial' will be unlocked last. \!First, let's clear
the 'three' trials!

\SE[51]There are spirits at the deepest part of the trials! So,
please do various things there and make it feel good!!
\SE[54]...That's all! Dismissed!!
